videoSnippet.title: Can you Find the Move Bobby Fischer used to Crush Benko?
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Robert James Fischer vs Pal Benko
"Break the Benko" 
USA-ch (1965), New York, NY USA, rd 4, Dec-17 
Spanish Game: Closed Variations. Breyer Defense (C95)
